=== Examples

Show all time zones:

  <%= executable %>:zones

Show names of times zones with an offset to the local time zone:

  <%= executable %>:zones 12
  <%= executable %>:zones -8
  <%= executable %>:zones 6:30

Filter time zones for a country by passing a two-letter country code:

  <%= executable %>:zones US
  <%= executable %>:zones JP
  <%= executable %>:zones KE

To show the system local time zones there is a subcommand:

  <%= executable %>:zones:local

For US time zones there is a subcommand:

  <%= executable %>:zones:us

Results can also be filtered by an offset:

  OFFSET=-7 <%= executable %>:zones:all
  OFFSET=-5 <%= executable %>:zones:us
  OFFSET=6  <%= executable %>:zones CN
